        Selling in Petrie Terrace 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(25,24,23,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Petrie Terrace is one of Brisbane's smallest and most distinctive heritage suburbs, with a tightly-held cottage market sitting on the CBD's western edge. Here is what sellers need to know about pricing, presentation and timing in 2026.
      </p>
